name: LOFT512
description: V4w.enko - "LOFT512" is one more component. The form is based on spherical voronoi tessellation and extrude of centers of segments with each other.  The structure shows the whole energy of the archetype which is used for the next step of creation.  The GLB 3D object type allows to play with  Augmented Reality mode to zoom, pan, rotate to see more perspectives.
